      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hello fellow monday users! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=14\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>I’m excited to share a new idea I’ve been exploring using <strong><a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/mondayai\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>mondayai</span></a></strong> and <strong><a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/ai\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>ai</span></a></strong>.</p>\n<p>Originally, I created a workflow that pushed a status update into the <strong>Due Date</strong> field.<br />\nHowever, I just realized there’s a better way: I can use the <strong>Week</strong> column and apply <strong>Custom AI</strong> on the <strong>Date</strong> column to automatically generate a <strong>Due Date</strong>.</p>\n<p>See the screenshots and Step-by-Step process below:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Add <strong>Week</strong> column to your board.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/8/b8eae53f0acf155d100c234b5a7c62c470b88e4b.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.41.01\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/8/b8eae53f0acf155d100c234b5a7c62c470b88e4b_2_345x237.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.41.01\" width=\"345\" height=\"237\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.41.01</span><span class=\"informations\">761×524 50.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>On your <strong>Date</strong> column, use Custom AI to grab a specific date from the <strong>Week</strong> column. In my example, I am requesting for the AI to grab the last Thursday date available in the <strong>Week</strong> column selection.<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/a/5ade8b33ea226447e87f7ca31558ab35d6acfe99.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.44.55\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/a/5ade8b33ea226447e87f7ca31558ab35d6acfe99.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.44.55\" width=\"237\" height=\"164\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.44.55</span><span class=\"informations\">475×328 23 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/1/f198a429234b3d01202ae63a543e7dbc20f73254.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.19\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/f/1/f198a429234b3d01202ae63a543e7dbc20f73254.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.19\" width=\"193\" height=\"183\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.19</span><span class=\"informations\">387×366 21 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/4/a4c27eff428dbd1677a8058130e0413a17db3036.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.57 1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/4/a4c27eff428dbd1677a8058130e0413a17db3036.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.57 1\" width=\"186\" height=\"222\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-08-04 at 13.45.57 1</span><span class=\"informations\">373×445 18.4 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You will now see that whenever you change the <strong>Week</strong> column, you’ll also change the <strong>Date</strong> column.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"video-placeholder-container\">\n  </div><p></p>\n<p>Happy date-ing! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/laughing.png?v=14\" title=\":laughing:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":laughing:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>"
